These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, prince, old-henry, havana, tiparillo, vegafina
City: hamburg, hannover, venice, prague, london, paris
 1. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4
 2. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is not the person traveling to london##6
 4. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5
 5. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
 6. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
 7. the person traveling to london is not the prince-smoker##6
 8. the person traveling to paris is in an odd position##4
 9. the bongani-smoker is somewhere between the person traveling to paris and the havana-smoker##7
10. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
11. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
12. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
13. the person traveling to hamburg is the bongani-smoker##1
14. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5
15. the vegafina-smoker is the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Cigar   | havana   | bongani | old-henry   | vegafina     | prince    | tiparillo   |
| City           | london | hamburg   | paris | prague | venice | hannover |

