.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, coffee, 7up, juice, milk
House: palace, victorian, art-deco, farmhouse, craftsman, cape-cod
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 2. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 3. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 7. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person drinking juice is not the craftsman house##6
10. the palace house is somewhere between the cape-cod house and the farmhouse house##7
11. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
12. the person drinking milk is on the right of the victorian house##1
13. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
14. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4
15. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5
16. the cape-cod house is on the right of the palace house##1
17. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the victorian house and the person drinking juice##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Beverage   | water | milk | 7up | juice     | coffee      | almond-milk |
| House           | victorian         | art-deco        | craftsman   | farmhouse | palace | cape-cod    |

