.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, papaya, mango, apricot, kiwi, eggplant
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: may, february, march, july, november, october
 1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 2. the person eating broccoli is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is not the person eating apricot##6
 5. the person eating broccoli is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the left of the person eating eggplant##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
10. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere between the person eating kiwi and the person eating papaya##7
11. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
13. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
14. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Food   | kiwi        | apricot | eggplant    | broccoli    | mango | papaya |
| Birthday      | february | november  | october | july | may | march      |

