.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-4::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  manager, dancer, scientist, fisherman, dressmaker, chef
There are 6 different favourite colors: apricot, lavender, grey, amber, blue, black
 1. the chef is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 2. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the manager##3
 3. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the right of the dressmaker##5
 4. the manager is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 5. the person who likes lavender is not the dressmaker##6
 6. the scientist is somewhere between the chef and the dressmaker##7
 7. the scientist is somewhere between the manager and the chef##7
 8. the dancer is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 9. the person who likes apricot is somewhere between the scientist and the fisherman##7
10. the person who likes amber is on the right of the fisherman##1
11. the dressmaker is on the right of the scientist##1
12. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lavender##5
13. the person who likes grey is the fisherman##1
14. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the left of the manager##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Job      | fisherman | dancer | chef | scientist | dressmaker | manager   |
| Color   | grey  | amber      | apricot | blue     | black | lavender |

