.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-19::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: sailing, surfing, rugby, water-polo, golf, biathlon
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: january, december, march, october, august, june
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
12. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's birthday is in december##7
13. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Sport         | surfing   | golf | sailing      | water-polo | biathlon  | rugby   |
| Birthday   | october | june  | december | january   | august | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, motorbike, tram, snowmobile, airplane
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, chaman, baccarat, bolivar, game, davidoff
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the baccarat-smoker##5
 4. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the bolivar-smoker and the chaman-smoker##7
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
 6. the person driving the motorbike is the game-smoker##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the bolivar-smoker##5
 8. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 9. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the baccarat-smoker##5
10. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the davidoff-smoker##5
11. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
12. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the bolivar-smoker##5
13. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the motorbike##7
14. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
15. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Transport   | motorbike         | tram | skateboard | scooter   | airplane | snowmobile  |
| Cigar     | game | bolivar  | baccarat  | davidoff | chaman  | alhambra |

 